    <h1>API Documentation</h1>
    
    <h2>GET /image</h2>
    <p>Fetch a random image related to the search term from Pixabay.</p>
    <h3>Query Parameters:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>image</strong> (string): The search term for the image you want to fetch.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Example Request:</h3>
    <pre><code>GET /image?image=mountain</code></pre>

