    <h3>Error Responses:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><code>{ "error": "Please enter a valid text." }</code> - If the `image` parameter is missing or empty.</li>
        <li><code>{ "error": "No images found." }</code> - If no images are found for the given search term.</li>
        <li><code>{ "error": "Error message from the server" }</code> - If there is an issue with the request (e.g., API key error, network issues).</li>
    </ul>

